data.description: Welcome to your future home! This exceptional home offers more than just 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. You'll love the formal dining and formal living room which is separate from the family room giving your growing family the space you've been looking for. You have the option of turning that formal living room into an office space or craft room or to whatever fit your need. This split-plan home also offers a spacious kitchen, open to the family room and dinette area. It's perfect for keeping your guest entertained while preparing that gourmet dish for everyone to enjoy. The covered patio area overlooking the backyard is great for the next barbeque! Don't wait to schedule your showing, call today. This is home is a must see. Located minutes away from I-95, beaches, restaurants, and shopping centers.
